<br>
I do not wish to use two styles that go off evade, but rather, one style that does acceptable damage, effect, or both. My preferance (less chance of missing, since I tend to miss a lot).<br>
<br>
&quot;Mercenaries tend to have subpar performance until they reach higher realm ranks, particularly with RvR survivability. Lacking the higher amounts of evade that the other light tanks have, we start to come even with them after being able to afford to augment ourselves with realm abilities.&quot;<br>
<br>
Evade, along with others things i'm sure you're aware of. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Does this mean you agree our evade I isn't enough (or, at least, accept the possibility thereof)?<br>
<br>
The more I read other teamleaders posts and what-not, the more I grow a sense of joy that ours is just so.. effective. Not to put the others down, but k8t has that winning edge (and no, not talking about her upper life-afferming units - perverts <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )<br>
